{"tid":1721672,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【政見不合】趙詠瑤父母退出家庭群組：Family就不再是Family了","createTime":"2019-11-14T17:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T05:25:25.000Z","uid":119568,"like":107,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0f29282160fe8c8786d03fad933d5b8ebe4666fc","tid":1721672,"uid":119568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:11:31.000Z","msg":"參加過ViuTV《美選D.n.A》的人妻趙詠瑤（Kimi）自反送中運動以來，一直敢於表態，雖然政治表態一定會影響收入，但她表示太多濫暴事件，為良知都要站出來，否認過不到自己那一關，她更說：「希望大家唔好再蒙蔽自己對眼同隻耳仔，話畀自己聽眼前嘅嘢都係假&hellip;&hellip;一切都係切切實實存在、發生緊！」<br />\n<br />\n之不過相比之下，失去了賺錢機會當然感到徬徨，但事實上有不少人因政見不同而反目，即使家人、好朋友都一樣。今日Kimi在IG貼了一張背影相並留言：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「我的藍絲父母離開了Family的WhatsApp群了&hellip;&hellip;罪名是『不孝順』&hellip;&hellip;人性不懂，卻懂叫我孝順&hellip;&hellip;沒關係！我選擇了人性&hellip;&hellip;Family stand for Father and mother I love you&hellip;&hellip;但是他們選擇自己把FAM刪除的&hellip;&hellip;那Family就不再是Family了&hellip;&hellip;」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\nKimi今日接受《蘋果》訪問，她說：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「我其實真係冇乜可以同佢哋講，最初我覺得佢哋係支持，因為佢哋覺得警察有做錯嘅嘢，政府都有做錯嘅嘢</span></span>，所以都唔可以話佢哋完全係藍。但係我發覺香港大部份嘅打工仔一樣，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">都係好自私，覺得佢哋返工真係大晒，阻到佢哋就係你問題，而家去到呢個位，係學生嘅生死都唔去理，做人做到咁真係好自私</span></span>，為咗自己一個人嘅快樂，全部人死晒都唔介意，我唔明仲點可以喺呢個屋企生存落去？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191114/60267660\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191114%2F60267660&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc602FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=12f5d9fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191114%2F60267660&h=378d6978\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191114/60267660</a><br />\n<br />\n手足，不孤單呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />藍絲老豆老母講嘢真係好撚難聽"},{"pid":"3110a978fe1ebe099de9e48137354a61364dfa27","tid":1721672,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:11:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">入去retweet like reply</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Twitter吹大雞！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">！！！McConnell支持法案，重點推 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatemajldr/status/1195006159679299584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatemajldr%2Fstatus%2F1195006159679299584&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc602FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=476b6f94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatemajldr%2Fstatus%2F1195006159679299584&h=8c1d25b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senatemajldr/status/1195006159679299584</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Rick 多謝 McConnell <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1195011922799804416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1195011922799804416&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc602FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=95ba7d09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1195011922799804416&h=d2960883\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1195011922799804416</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Hawley 多謝 McConnell<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hawleymo/status/1194998439723065345\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhawleymo%2Fstatus%2F1194998439723065345&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc602FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=8e6a9571\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhawleymo%2Fstatus%2F1194998439723065345&h=07e17f14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hawleymo/status/1194998439723065345</a><br />\n<br />\n！！同埋多謝 Rubio 啊<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senrubiopress/status/1195016660350099456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenrubiopress%2Fstatus%2F1195016660350099456&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc602FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=311dada0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenrubiopress%2Fstatus%2F1195016660350099456&h=1ee7ed4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senrubiopress/status/1195016660350099456</a><br />\n<br />\n更加多嘅任務同link去 @TwitterHelpBot，admin團隊會繼續更新。"},{"pid":"7f4d12d6eb285f02b076a5feb6c7c307f17bc583","tid":1721672,"uid":183358,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:20:53.000Z","msg":"Who？"},{"pid":"a2d1c17be367f7d7de4c1aea17ecc8f613c4aaae","tid":1721672,"uid":24853,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:45:22.000Z","msg":"今晚就j你"},{"pid":"6222ca7c739c1985448aa02dbe5d4b7869031f04","tid":1721672,"uid":114097,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:48:40.000Z","msg":"我啱啱相反<br />\n退晒啲Family 群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一向要做就做屋企最大聲嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e6cdfd5a4c66bcdfa93a5e5912380dd07af3017","tid":1721672,"uid":173060,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"6222ca7c739c1985448aa02dbe5d4b7869031f04","tid":1721672,"uid":114097,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:48:40.000Z","msg":"我啱啱相反<br />\n退晒啲Family 群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一向要做就做屋企最大聲嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T17:51:45.000Z","msg":"有港豬有藍<br />\n我有幾次嬲到想退<br />\n之後諗諗下唔係，只要佢地次次一send埋d示威者唔岩既野我就send返d 癲狗亂咬普通市民既片出黎<br />\n之後個個無人出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355042574308092362a0e3d49b66ff31046172e4","tid":1721672,"uid":254461,"